name: ProtoPrototype
description:
Want to double jump? you can.

Collectibles? you have them.

Slow Mo? there is on EVERY enemy you get down.

RPG Life/Stamina bar? present.

Random objectives generation? try to beat the game once.

 

Quick all-in prototype to have fun around multiple game mechanics, all in one level and one minute to shoot every collectible, except enemy won’t stop coming for you.

One of my first shipped prototype, with lots of feature.
